        "content": "<p>With <a href=\"https://docs.makie.org/dev/reference/blocks/axis#xtickformat\"><code>xtickformat</code></a> and <code>Dates.unix2datetime</code> it should be possible to display labels in human-readable form.</p>\n<p>Otherwise, the Makie <a href=\"https://docs.makie.org/stable/#Getting-Help\">Getting help</a> section states that usage questions are best directed to discourse, so you might have better luck there.</p>",
